Subject: EPP Server appliance is running on low on free space
Description:
The system partition on the Hard Drive / Disk of your EPP Server appliance is running on low on free space.
To address this we were advised that a Netwrix tech needs to schedule a remote session and check what is utilizing the space on the system partition and if necessary perform a cleanup.
Please advise a date and time to have such a session?

Regards,
Shaheed.
Solution_Comment__c: Solved in a remote session where we empty the journal from /var/log/journal.
